originalText.text: WiFi was the only accurate item in post. Come in with very low expectations before considering this apartment. I only took room as location was centrally located to New Year's Eve events and activities. Bring your own cleaning supplies because these apartments are filthy. You will find loose hair, used personal hygiene items, dust mounds, rust, peeling paint, open heating grates, and disrepair everywhere in the apartment. Electric sockets are painted over and inoperable. Bed is hard, uncomfortable, and full of stray hairs so bring your items to clean. Wear night mask and earplugs as no room darkening shade and loud neighbors. Wear warm night clothes as heater may not be functional. Open heater grate rusty and dusty. Cannot lock your room so do not bring valuable items on your trip. Positive is that is centrally located. That depends which random location he sends to you when you arrive as location listed is not where you will be staying. Need to call the host several times as he does not have voicemail set up on phone, did not respond to SMS messages, and did not respond to email through app until well after check in time. Find warm places to stay when you contact host to avoid freezing in winter for long response time.
